        "timestamp": "2019-04-23 16:41:40.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nWould be happy to add something like kubernetes cluster healthcheck, after this change.\nReasoning is that rke actually does ectd/kubelet/whatever healthchecks, but does not healthcheck pods in kube-system. Not sure how important it is for us to check that, the main source of error there is missing docker images. like dashboard or whatever images.",
